name='description' content='Professional Photographers of America (PPA) is the world&#039;s largest non-profit photography association organized for professional photographers with more than 30,000 creative members in more than 50 countries. PPA is your go-to resource to grow your photography business and make it more profitable. Whether you photography niche is wedding photography, drone photography, senior portrait photography, food photography or pet photography, we have photography education, classes, sales and marketing tools and contracts for you. Camera equipment insurance and data-loss protection come with your PPA membership so you are protected from the start.' /><meta
